name: a little cell
description:
Dear diary, 

Sometimes I feel small, very small. Like a little dot in this galaxy, do I have something special?   Am I more than just a blob of cells? I don’t have all the answers (hell I don’t know shit hahah). I’m just existing and trying to figure out what the fuck is going on! 👁👄👁 

Maybe I’m in this parallel universe where little cells are more than little cells. A  different dimension where I can create anything I want... after all I don’t know what will happen. I’m just here for the ride I guess 🍃

I have the power to be
I have the power to create
I have the power to explore 
I have the power to learn
